# Installation errors
E13000 = The system has already been initialized.
E13001 = Username is required.
E13002 = Email address is required.
E13003 = Password is required.
E13004 = Domain is required.
E13005 = The domain is invalid. It must not contain spaces and must include at least one dot.
E13006 = The email address is invalid.
E13007 = That username is already taken.
E13008 = That email address is already registered.
E13009 = The key algorithm is not supported.
